{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hyper Frenzy - Arena Space Shooter</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hyper Frenzy is an arena space shooter for casual gameplay. Blast up some enemy ships on various space themed maps. Choose between your favorite game mode such as versus, team-versus or hidenseek. Use up to 10 different weapons, each with their own advantages and disadvantages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653360/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1730393319\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is especially suited for quick local matches against bots in a space setting. It's very simplistic, but yet this is exactly what provides you with much fun during casual gameplay sessions. Protip: Use the radar to see where your opponents are in order to seek and destroy them. Good luck, pilot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653360/extras/features.png?t=1730393319\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Casual arena space battles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Various game modes such as versus, team-versus or hidenseek</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Different themed arenas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10 different weapons to use </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Various items to collect to get an advantage during combat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653360/extras/worlds.png?t=1730393319\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Orbit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Starsystem</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ThreePlanets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vortex</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p cla